reviewText: Not the sellers fault, just crappy movies
Joelando great as mysterious bad guy.  Very hot..
WHO CAN RESIST AN 8 PACKAGE OF 8 MURDER MOVIES?
Totally Awesome product (8-Movie Murder at Midnight 1), especially the one w/Joe Lando!!! :-)  Joe Lando is such an incredible handsome actor!! :-)
I bought this for Joe Lando. Have not watched any other movies on these DVDs. Mr. Lando exudes sexuality and you always wonder if he did or didn't do it. Perfect for a weekend watching party!
